response yet):<br>
<br>
I've been having this same problem since the last patch. Every time I use my evade social that has about 3 doability's in it, I'm not able to left click anything, AND I'm not able to use any of my other abilites on my hot keys, like Backstab! When I hit &quot;1&quot; to backstab, I get a message &quot;You can't use that command right now...&quot;. That lasts for quite a few minutes (like 5-10) or until one of my weapons proc (pretty weird), or I zone. I play in the full-screen overlay mode, and I noticed that you get that same message when trying to use hot keys when your are banking or selling.<br>
<br>
I also noticed that my first ability after the &quot;/attack off&quot; will work, but the next one won't. For expample, this is from my logs when I had my social set up as<br>
/attack off<br>
/do &lt;beg&gt;<br>
/do &lt;steal&gt;<br>
/do &lt;hide/evade&gt;<br>
<br>
[Mon Mar 19 03:15:50 2001] Your attempt at begging was unsuccessful.<br>
[Mon Mar 19 03:15:50 2001] You must wait longer before you can attempt to steal.<br>
[Mon Mar 19 03:15:50 2001] A froglok tal shaman tries to hit YOU, but misses!<br>
[Mon Mar 19 03:15:50 2001] You begin to hide...<br>
[Mon Mar 19 03:15:50 2001] You have momentarily ducked away from the main combat.<br>
<br>
Then I hit &quot;1&quot; to backstab and:<br>
[Mon Mar 19 03:15:51 2001] You can't use that command right now...<br>
<br>
This has happend with a different set of abilities in there too:<br>
/attack off<br>
/do &lt;sense traps&gt;<br>
/do &lt;beg&gt;<br>
/do &lt;hide/evade&gt;<br>
/attack on<br>
<br>
[Sun Mar 18 21:14:12 2001] You do not Sense any traps.<br>
[Sun Mar 18 21:14:12 2001] You must wait longer before you can attempt to beg.<br>
[Sun Mar 18 21:14:13 2001] You begin to hide...<br>
[Sun Mar 18 21:14:13 2001] Your attempts at ducking clear of combat fail.<br>
[Sun Mar 18 21:14:14 2001] You have moved and are no longer hidden!!<br>
<br>
Then hot key &quot;1&quot;:<br>
[Sun Mar 18 21:14:14 2001] You can't use that command right now...<br>
<br>
A monk was having a similar problem with 0 casting time items (like the monk epic item) being activated from a hot key slot.<br>
<br>
I took beg out of my hot key macro and the problem stopped. If they wanted to nerf beg this way, that's ok, but causing every hot key AND F1-F10 keys (execpt F7 and F8 ) AND left clicking to be disabled is a pretty serious bug IMO. <p><strong>
